  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-6">
          What Are Calendar Insights?
        </h2>
        <div
          class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-muted leading-relaxed"
        >
          <p>
            Calendar insights give you a simple overview of your appointment
            activity and scheduling patterns. Instead of manually tracking
            meetings or reviewing your calendar day by day, CalendHub
            automatically shows you basic statistics like how many appointments
            you have each week, which days are busiest, and how your schedule
            changes over time. These insights are built directly into your
            calendar management platform, so you can see appointment trends
            without using separate tracking tools or spreadsheets.
          </p>

          <p>
            Your calendar already contains information about every meeting and
            appointment you schedule. CalendHub's insights feature simply
            organizes this information into easy-to-read summaries and
            visualizations. See weekly totals, compare busy weeks to light
            weeks, identify your typical busiest days, and understand how time
            is distributed across your different calendars. The system
            automatically tracks this data as you use your calendar normally -
            no manual input, timers, or extra steps required.
          </p>

          <p>
            Unlike standalone time tracking applications that require you to
            categorize activities or run background software, CalendHub's
            calendar insights work with the scheduling data you're already
            creating. View simple metrics about meeting frequency, average
            durations, and time allocation across work and personal calendars.
            Track patterns over time to see how your schedule evolves from month
            to month. All insights are based on your calendar events, giving you
            a straightforward view of your appointment activity without
            complicated analytics dashboards or advanced reporting features.
          </p>

          <p>
            Privacy and data security are important when viewing calendar
            information. CalendHub only displays insights based on your own
            calendar events - the basic metadata like event times, durations,
            and which calendar they belong to. No meeting content, notes, or
            sensitive details are analyzed. You control which calendars are
            included in your insights, and all data remains private and
            encrypted. This simple, privacy-focused approach gives you
            visibility into your scheduling patterns without exposing
            confidential information or requiring complex permissions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

