            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-4">
              Simple Calendar Activity Tracking
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
              CalendHub's insights feature works by organizing the basic
              information from your calendar events - times, durations, and
              which calendar they belong to. As you schedule appointments
              throughout the week, the system keeps running totals and
              identifies simple patterns like which days tend to fill up first
              or how many meetings you typically have. Historical data shows how
              your schedule looked in previous weeks or months for easy
              comparison. All information is stored securely with encryption,
              and only displays data from calendars you've connected to
              CalendHub.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
